title: Taylor Swift | GOP and Fox News Lie About the Economy Under Biden vs. Trump: A Closer Look
description:
Seth takes a closer look at the GOP and Fox News lying about the state of the economy under Joe Biden and attempting to purge anyone who dared to vote for a bipartisan infrastructure bill from their ranks.

Then, Taylor Swift talks about reuniting with her band, wanting to own her own music and experiencing nostalgia with her fans for her album Red (Taylor's Version).
